my-claw/sdp/prd-songwriter-emsd-completion.md:152:| SWE-004 | Add a richer song-form library and deformation system for recognizable but varied forms. | MUST | T1 | - form grammar includes verse/chorus-like, AABA-like, build/drop, ambient arc, rondo/return, bridge, afterglow, and through-composed families expressed as section functions<br/>- form selection avoids recent-form fatigue from repertoire memory<br/>- tests verify valid form complexity for `micro`, `song`, `extended`, and `suite` classes |
