docs/command-reference.md:190:- The live songwriter stack is now present end to end: `reharmonizer.py` supplies section functions and cadence types, `hook_engine.py` adds deterministic titles/hooks/phrase-pairs, `arrangement_engine.py` shapes scene-level groove and density, `practice_curriculum.py` chooses the current away-mode lab, `ear_engine.py` scores performed notes at the end of each song, and `repertoire_memory.py` stores promoted song-level memories instead of only short fragments.
